org.gradoop.storage.common.api

Interface EPGMGraphOutput

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    EPGMGraphPredictableOutput<GFilter,VFilter,EFilter>

    public interface EPGMGraphOutput
    Definition of graph store output. A graph input instance provide a set of query methods for EPGM Elements both id query and traversal query are supported
